  "description": "<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Description: </strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">As an Special Projects Intern at SNITCH, you will be at the forefront of our business management, responsible for implementing solutions to bring efficiency across the supply chain</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Skill sets: </strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Advanced Excel,SQL Supply Chain Management</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Responsibilities:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">As an Operations Intern - Special Projects at SNITCH, you will be at the forefront of our business management, responsible for:</span></p><p><br></p><ul><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">End-to-End Business Management:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> You'll be the driving force behind planning, monitoring, and creating dashboards to establish a solid review and feedback mechanism.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Data-Driven Solutions</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Devising data-driven action plans to quickly address escalations from field teams, warehouse,partners, and stakeholders.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Continuous Improvement:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Monitoring and enhancing daily operations, deploying and building processes based on our business goals and key metrics.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Collaboration:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Coordinating with the field operations team to implement operational and strategic initiatives, all while developing clear work plans.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">System and Process Building</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Ensuring that all systems in the warehouse and operations function seamlessly while aligning with our high-quality standards.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Compliance and Efficiency:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Building processes that not only meet our business objectives but also ensure compliance with industry standards.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">On-Ground Availability:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> You'll be the hands-on leader who is readily available on the ground, not hesitating to solve problems and set things up from the ground.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Customer-Centric:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Delivering exceptional customer experiences through on-ground and remote setups.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Data Expertise:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Utilising strong data visualisation and evaluation skills to transform data into actionable insights and recommendations.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">SOP Implementation</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Designing, documenting, and implementing Standard Operating Procedures (SOPs) to enhance process robustness.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Process Adherenc</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">e: Working with operations teams to guarantee that stakeholders adhere to standardised processes, as per the process playbook.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Bridge Builder</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Being a constant bridge between the ground operations team and other functions such as Business Development, Tech, and Finance.</span></li></ul><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Skills Required:</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">An in-depth understanding of specific supply chain functions, such as procurement and transportation, and the ability to communicate your expertise clearly.</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Exposure to various supply chain functions, from procurement to retailing.</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Proficiency in supply chain software and solutions to engage clients effectively.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Strategic Thinker</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Exceptional problem-solving and analytical skills.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Collaborative:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> The ability to coordinate seamlessly with cross-functional teams.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Adaptability</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Willingness to work in a highly ambiguous environment with a strong bias for action.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Initiative</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: The ability to develop, execute, improvise, and enhance 0-1 building and growth initiatives.</span></li><li><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Pace-Setter: </strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Thriving in a fast-paced and ambiguous environment.</span></li></ul><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Supply Chain Domain Knowledge: You should possess:</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">These skills are essential to succeed in this role</strong></p>",
